ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
Subject(wheat, amber durum wheat, Canadian Western red winter wheat, (eastward and westward bound) feed barley and designated barley) Freight Adjustment Factors ** APPROVAL THEREOF **
PrecisOrder approving the amounts established by the Canadian Wheat Board of the FREIGHT ADJUSTMENT FACTORS for certain delivery points for WHEAT, RED WINTER WHEAT, AMBER DURUM WHEAT, FEED BARLEY and DESIGNATED BARLEY to be delivered to The Canadian Wheat Board during the 2011-2012 pool period, beginning August 1, 2011 and ending on July 31, 2012.
